{"word":"καταλείπω","slug":"καταλείπω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰαταλείπω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κατά\">κατά</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:λείπω\">λείπω</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp> leave (behind)<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> through withdrawal, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> or things left in place <b><a href='B:470 16:4'>Mt 16:4</a>; <a href='B:470 19:5'>19:5</a>; <a href='B:470 21:17'>21:17</a>; <a href='B:480 10:7'>Mk 10:7</a>; <a href='B:480 14:52'>14:52</a>; <a href='B:490 5:28'>Lk 5:28</a>; <a href='B:490 15:4'>15:4</a>; <a href='B:510 18:19'>Ac 18:19</a>; <a href='B:510 24:27'>24:27</a>; <a href='B:510 25:14'>25:14</a>; <a href='B:560 5:31'>Eph 5:31</a>; <a href='B:590 3:1'>1 Th 3:1</a>.—</b>A place <b><a href='B:470 4:13'>Mt 4:13</a>; <a href='B:510 21:3'>Ac 21:3</a>; <a href='B:650 11:27'>Hb 11:27</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> through death <b><a href='B:480 12:19'>Mk 12:19</a>, <a href='B:480 12:21'>21</a>; <a href='B:490 20:31'>Lk 20:31</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘cause to be left over’, <b>retain <a href='B:520 11:4'>Ro 11:4</a>; remain in force <a href='B:650 4:1'>Hb 4:1</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:κατάλειμμα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:καταλελειμμένος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}